001package io.github.ai4ci.config.refdata;
002
003import java.nio.file.Paths;
004
005import javax.annotation.Nullable;
006
007import org.immutables.value.Value;
008
009import io.github.ai4ci.Import;
010import io.github.ai4ci.util.Factor;
011import io.github.ai4ci.util.Repository;
012import io.github.ai4ci.util.Repository.Indexed;
013
014@Value.Style(
015                deepImmutablesDetection = false,
016                passAnnotations = { Import.class, Import.Id.class },
017                get = { "is*", "get*" }
018)
019public class UKCensus {
020
021        @Value.Immutable
022        @Import("AgeGender.csv")
023        public static interface AgeGender extends Indexed<AgeGender> {
024                double getAge();
025                int getCount();
026                Gender getGender();
027                Geography getGeography();
028                @Import.Id
029                String getId();
030                int getTotal();
031        }
032
033        @Value.Immutable
034        @Import("Commuting.csv")
035        public static interface Commuting extends Indexed<Commuting> {
036                CommutingType getCommutingType();
037                int getCount();
038                Geography getGeography();
039                @Import.Id
040                String getId();
041                int getTotal();
042        }
043
044        public static enum CommutingType implements Factor {
045                @Level("Bicycle") BICYCLE,
046                @Level("Bus, minibus or coach") BUS_MINIBUS_OR_COACH,
047                @Level("Driving a car or van") DRIVING_A_CAR_OR_VAN,
048                @Level("Motorcycle, scooter or moped") MOTORCYCLE_SCOOTER_OR_MOPED,
049                @Level("On foot") ON_FOOT,
050                @Level("Other method of travel to work") OTHER_METHOD_OF_TRAVEL_TO_WORK,
051                @Level("Passenger in a car or van") PASSENGER_IN_A_CAR_OR_VAN,
052                @Level("Taxi") TAXI, @Level("Train") TRAIN,
053                @Level(
054                        "Underground, metro, light rail, tram"
055                ) UNDERGROUND_METRO_LIGHT_RAIL_TRAM,
056                @Level("Work mainly at or from home") WORK_MAINLY_AT_OR_FROM_HOME
057        }
058
059        @Value.Immutable
060        @Import("Distances.csv")
061        public static interface Distances extends Indexed<Distances> {
062                double getDistance();
063
064                @Import.Id
065                String getId();
066
067                Geography getSourceGeography();
068
069                Geography getTargetGeography();
070        }
071
072        public static enum Employment implements Factor {
073                @Level("In employment") IN_EMPLOYMENT,
074                @Level("Long-term sick or disabled") LONG_TERM_SICK_OR_DISABLED,
075                @Level("Looking after home or family") LOOKING_AFTER_HOME_OR_FAMILY,
076                @Level("Other") OTHER, @Level("Retired") RETIRED,
077                @Level("Student") STUDENT, @Level("Unemployed") UNEMPLOYED
078        }
079
080        public static enum EmploymentType implements Factor {
081                @Level("Employee") EMPLOYEE,
082                @Level("Self-employed with employees") SELF_EMPLOYED_WITH_EMPLOYEES,
083                @Level("Self-employed without employees") SELF_EMPLOYED_WITHOUT_EMPLOYEES
084        }
085
086        @Value.Immutable
087        @Import("Ethnicity.csv")
088        public static interface Ethnicity extends Indexed<Ethnicity> {
089                int getCount();
090
091                Geography getGeography();
092
093                Group getGroup();
094
095                @Import.Id
096                String getId();
097
098                @Nullable
099                Subgroup getSubgroup();
100
101                int getTotal();
102        }
103
104        public static enum FullTime implements Factor {
105                @Level("Full") FULL, @Level("Part") PART
106        }
107
108        public static enum Gender implements Factor {
109                @Level("Female") FEMALE, @Level("Male") MALE
110        }
111
112        @Value.Immutable
113        @Import("Geography.csv")
114        public static interface Geography extends Indexed<Geography> {
115                @Import.Id
116                String getId();
117
118                String getName();
119        }
120
121        public static enum Group implements Factor {
122                @Level(
123                        "Asian, Asian British or Asian Welsh"
124                ) ASIAN_ASIAN_BRITISH_OR_ASIAN_WELSH,
125                @Level(
126                        "Black, Black British, Black Welsh, Caribbean or African"
127                ) BLACK_BLACK_BRITISH_BLACK_WELSH_CARIBBEAN_OR_AFRICAN,
128                @Level("Mixed or Multiple ethnic groups") MIXED_OR_MULTIPLE_ETHNIC_GROUPS,
129                @Level("Other ethnic group") OTHER_ETHNIC_GROUP, @Level("White") WHITE
130        }
131
132        @Value.Immutable
133        @Import("Industry.csv")
134        public static interface Industry extends Indexed<Industry> {
135                int getCount();
136
137                Geography getGeography();
138
139                @Import.Id
140                String getId();
141
142                IndustryName getIndustryName();
143
144                int getTotal();
145        }
146
147        public static enum IndustryName implements Factor {
148                @Level(
149                        "Accommodation and food service activities"
150                ) ACCOMMODATION_AND_FOOD_SERVICE_ACTIVITIES,
151                @Level(
152                        "Administrative and support service activities"
153                ) ADMINISTRATIVE_AND_SUPPORT_SERVICE_ACTIVITIES,
154                @Level(
155                        "Agriculture, Forestry and fishing"
156                ) AGRICULTURE_FORESTRY_AND_FISHING, @Level("Construction") CONSTRUCTION,
157                @Level("Education") EDUCATION,
158                @Level(
159                        "Electricity, gas, steam and air conditioning supply"
160                ) ELECTRICITY_GAS_STEAM_AND_AIR_CONDITIONING_SUPPLY,
161                @Level(
162                        "Financial and insurance activities"
163                ) FINANCIAL_AND_INSURANCE_ACTIVITIES,
164                @Level(
165                        "Human health and social work activities"
166                ) HUMAN_HEALTH_AND_SOCIAL_WORK_ACTIVITIES,
167                @Level("Information and communication") INFORMATION_AND_COMMUNICATION,
168                @Level("Manufacturing") MANUFACTURING,
169                @Level("Mining and quarrying") MINING_AND_QUARRYING,
170                @Level(
171                        "Professional, scientific and technical activities"
172                ) PROFESSIONAL_SCIENTIFIC_AND_TECHNICAL_ACTIVITIES,
173                @Level(
174                        "Public administration and defence; compulsory social security"
175                ) PUBLIC_ADMINISTRATION_AND_DEFENCE_COMPULSORY_SOCIAL_SECURITY,
176                @Level("Real estate activities") REAL_ESTATE_ACTIVITIES,
177                @Level("Transport and storage") TRANSPORT_AND_STORAGE,
178                @Level(
179                        "Water supply; Sewerage, Waste management and Remediation activities"
180                ) WATER_SUPPLY_SEWERAGE_WASTE_MANAGEMENT_AND_REMEDIATION_ACTIVITIES,
181                @Level(
182                        "Wholesale and retail trade; repair of motor vehicles and motorcycles"
183                ) WHOLESALE_AND_RETAIL_TRADE_REPAIR_OF_MOTOR_VEHICLES_AND_MOTORCYCLES
184        }
185
186        public static enum Student implements Factor {
187                @Level(
188                        "active (excluding full-time students)"
189                ) ACTIVE_EXCLUDING_FULL_TIME_STUDENTS,
190                @Level("active and a full-time student") ACTIVE_AND_A_FULL_TIME_STUDENT,
191                @Level("inactive") INACTIVE
192        }
193
194        public static enum Subgroup implements Factor {
195                @Level("African") AFRICAN,
196                @Level("Any other ethnic group") ANY_OTHER_ETHNIC_GROUP,
197                @Level("Arab") ARAB, @Level("Bangladeshi") BANGLADESHI,
198                @Level("Caribbean") CARIBBEAN, @Level("Chinese") CHINESE,
199                @Level(
200                        "English, Welsh, Scottish, Northern Irish or British"
201                ) ENGLISH_WELSH_SCOTTISH_NORTHERN_IRISH_OR_BRITISH,
202                @Level("Gypsy or Irish Traveller") GYPSY_OR_IRISH_TRAVELLER,
203                @Level("Indian") INDIAN, @Level("Irish") IRISH,
204                @Level("Other Asian") OTHER_ASIAN, @Level("Other Black") OTHER_BLACK,
205                @Level(
206                        "Other Mixed or Multiple ethnic groups"
207                ) OTHER_MIXED_OR_MULTIPLE_ETHNIC_GROUPS,
208                @Level("Other White") OTHER_WHITE, @Level("Pakistani") PAKISTANI,
209                @Level("Roma") ROMA, @Level("White and Asian") WHITE_AND_ASIAN,
210                @Level("White and Black African") WHITE_AND_BLACK_AFRICAN,
211                @Level("White and Black Caribbean") WHITE_AND_BLACK_CARIBBEAN
212        }
213
214        @Value.Immutable
215        @Import("Unemployment.csv")
216        public static interface Unemployment extends Indexed<Unemployment> {
217                int getCount();
218
219                @Nullable
220                Employment getEmployment();
221
222                @Nullable
223                EmploymentType getEmploymentType();
224
225                @Nullable
226                FullTime getFullTime();
227
228                Geography getGeography();
229
230                @Import.Id
231                String getId();
232
233                Student getStudent();
234
235                int getTotal();
236        }
237
238        public static final Class<?>[] TYPES = new Class<?>[] { AgeGender.class,
239                        Commuting.class, Distances.class, Ethnicity.class, Geography.class,
240                        Industry.class, Unemployment.class };
241
242        public static Repository load() {
243                try {
244                        var path = Paths.get(
245                                        UKCensus.class.getClassLoader().getResource("UKCensus").toURI()
246                        );
247                        return Repository.loadAll(path, TYPES);
248                } catch (Exception e) {
249                        throw new RuntimeException(e);
250                }
251        }
252}
